(41, 6, 10, 42, 10, 7, 8, 'there abide till ye depart', 'Instructions for Hospitality', 'Both passages emphasize the importance of staying in one house and accepting what is offered. This connection highlights the directive to remain in a place until departure and to not move from house to house.', 'theme', 0.321, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
(41, 6, 10, 44, 16, 15, 15, 'abide till ye depart from that place', 'Hospitality and Abiding', 'This connection highlights the theme of hospitality and the instruction to abide in a house. Both passages emphasize the importance of staying in a designated place during their ministry.', 'theme', 0.314, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
(41, 6, 10, 44, 17, 5, 7, 'there abide till ye depart', 'Hospitality and Community Response', 'This connection highlights the theme of hospitality and the reactions of communities to those who enter their homes. In Mark, Jesus instructs his disciples to abide in the houses they enter, while in Acts, the community reacts strongly to the presence of believers in Jason''s house.', 'theme', 0.314, 'medium', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
